txt.en: 'Jangovar invaders yesterday, Easterling begging meals today? Enough!'
'Now is not the time for Dale to feed and shelter the needy!'
'Respectable Easterling merchants? Yes. Penniless beggars? No!'
'These new Easterlings have come far enough. Let them stay across the river.'
'Don't trust their rags. These new Easterlings are Jangovar in disguise!'
'They say they fled RhÃ»n. But why have they come here, of all places?'
